    "AI in education, in particular, ADWTs, calls for critical awareness of ethical protocols and requires collaborative efforts by AI experts, researchers, and educators to initiate extensive, longitudinal research (Zhang & Aslan 2021) that could generate more ethical guidelines for all stakeholders and spur new transformations and possibilities in education."
